      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Includes Bible record with slave births (5 leaves) and
         index (1 leaf). The record is a typed transcript. Areas
         covered are Nelson and Albemarle counties, Virginia. Other
         surnames mentioned are Blackenburg, Gregory, Horne, Oldham,
         Page, Stoneman, Taylor, Templeman, Ware and Whitten</p>
      </scopecontent>
